==On the Trail==
===Talking to the Khazard Barman===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Barman:''' Hi, what can I get you? We have a range of quality brews.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|quest=No|I'll have a beer please.}}
* {{topt|quest=No|I'd like a Khali Brew please.}}
